Ant. Remember not, O
Lord, our offences, nor those
of our parents, and take not
revenge on our sins.

Thou wilt bring my soul
out of trouble: and in thy
mercy, thou wilt destroy mine
enemies.

And thou wilt cut off all
them that afflict my soul: for
I am thy servant.
